  "title": "(Tampines) Office job - Shipping Coordinator",
  "description": "<h1>NO EXPERIENCE NEEDED</h1><ul><li>1 year renewable contract</li></ul><ul><li>Tampines East MRT / Changi North<br /></li><li>Monday to Friday, 8:30 AM to 5:30 PM, </li><li>Saturdays from 8:30 AM to 12:30 PM.</li></ul><p><br /><strong>Job Scope</strong></p><ul><li><p>Processing incoming customer orders from email and our business systems.</p></li><li><p>Accurately updating shipment and inventory data.</p></li><li><p>Preparing instructions for the warehouse team and coordinating daily tasks.</p></li><li><p>Scheduling deliveries and creating essential shipping documents.</p></li><li><p>Performing final checks to ensure accuracy and prevent delays.</p></li><li><p>Communicating clearly with customers, delivery partners, and your colleagues.</p></li><li><p>Keeping organized and compliant records for all transactions.</p></li></ul><ul><li><p>Hands-on experience in logistics, shipping, or order coordination.</p></li><li><p>Practical familiarity with business or warehouse management systems.</p></li></ul>",
